_json.title: Death and Nightingales - Season 1 Episode 1 | BBC Two
_json.description: Our story takes place on the day of Beth’s twenty-third birthday. Growing up, Beth found herself caught between two warring parents. She thinks back to the day when she was twelve years old and overheard an argument that revealed to her that the man she has always thought as ‘papa’, Billy Winters, is not her real father.
